{"tid":1714544,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣傳! 11.11 黎明行動懶人包! 紀錄多條恐怖片段流出!","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:31:56.000Z","uid":1806,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fe493b97887c89ec788a5af8b8728d2703f33591","tid":1714544,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/njwMiQEwxaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnjwMiQEwxaw&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE94E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=d1914af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/njwMiQEwxaw</a><br />\n<br />\n今次團隊整左近7分鐘懶人包短片，簡述左今日十一月十一日全港各區情況: 警察如何進入瘋狂狀態對待示威者，包括在清晨西灣河開3槍實彈，有兩人受槍傷；防暴警向中大理大校園施放催淚彈等等。此外，亦描述了警察對示威者如何濫用私刑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英語及外語版會盡快趕製上傳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1112 正在製作當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgy4m0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhgy4m0h.jpg&h=b1cc8e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港! 時代革命!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人反抗!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HKGETV Social Media Platform<br />\n<strong><blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE94E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7a710b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url